OL,3,CBritain facing a water scarcity
OL,4,Ccrisis. What is being done to prevent
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FHavant Thickett in Hampshire is the
OL,8,Fonly new reservoir where construction
OL,9,Fis already underway, but it is still
OL,10,Fat least seven years from being
OL,11,Foperational.
OL,13,FBob Taylor, CEO of Portsmouth Water,
OL,14,Fthe company behind the new reservoir
OL,15,Fat Havant Thickett told ITV News that
OL,16,Fa combination of climate change and a
OL,17,Flack of infrastructure means we are
OL,18,Flosing water.
