OL,3,CBritain facing a water scarcity
OL,4,Ccrisis. What is being done to prevent
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,F"Our whole water infrastructure is
OL,8,Fbuilt around the seasons - so high
OL,9,Frainfall in the winter time that is
OL,10,Fconserved through reservoirs and
OL,11,Fstorage" he said.
OL,13,F"That is then supplied during high
OL,14,Fdemand periods and dry periods in the
OL,15,Fsummer.
OL,17,F"But all of that has been turned on
OL,18,Fits head with much more intense
OL,19,Frainfall in seasons we don't expect.
OL,20,FThe runoff of that rainfall is then
OL,21,Fbeing lost to rivers and into the sea.
