OL,3,CBritain facing a water scarcity
OL,4,Ccrisis. What is being done to prevent
OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,F"We're not able to capture it because
OL,8,Fwe haven't been building reservoirs
OL,9,Ffor the last 30 years."
OL,11,FWater storage is not the only solution
OL,12,Fto the shortfall the nation is facing.
OL,14,FEven when all the new reservoirs are
OL,15,Fup and running, they will only make up
OL,16,Fa third of the predicted deficit.
OL,18,FOther savings will need to come from
OL,19,Ffixing leakages, moving water and
OL,20,Fimproving water efficiency.
