OL,7,FThe East and South East of England are
OL,8,Fparticularly water stressed. In the
OL,9,Ffuture, water will need to be moved
OL,10,Ffrom more plentiful places like Wales
OL,11,Fand areas of Northern England via a
OL,12,Fsystem of canals and other re-routing
OL,13,F` another huge project.
OL,15,FNearly two billion litres of the
OL,16,Fpredicted deficit will need to be made
OL,17,Fup for by a change in how we use our
OL,18,Fwater.
