OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FAll this has an impact on growth. The
OL,8,Fgovernment wants to build 1.5 million
OL,9,Fnew homes but some of their priority
OL,10,Fgrowth areas like Cambridge are
OL,11,Falready water stressed.
OL,13,FAnalysis done by Public First for ITV
OL,14,FNews shows that 27,000 of the planned
OL,15,Fnew homes will not be able to be built
OL,16,Fbecause they are planned for areas
OL,17,Fwhere there will not be enough water
OL,18,Fsupply. They estimate this will cost
OL,19,Fthe economy #11.7bn.
