OL,5,Cit?
OL,7,FChanges need to happen soon says
OL,8,FAlastair Chisholm, director of policy
OL,9,Fat the Chartered Institution of Water
OL,10,Fand Environmental Management: "The
OL,11,Fworst case scenario is there will not
OL,12,Fbe enough water available for the
OL,13,Fgovernment to supply new homes," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"This is a key plank of the
OL,17,Fgovernment's pledge to the electorate
OL,18,Fon growth. They want to deliver these
OL,19,Fhomes so they need to make sure water
OL,20,Fis not a barrier to that."
