OL,7,FIn Cambridge, a new development called
OL,8,FClay Farm could offer a glimpse of the
OL,9,Ffuture. Reed beds on the site capture
OL,10,Frainwater running off roads and roofs.
OL,11,FFrom there it is pumped or drained
OL,12,Finto a tank and then supplied to all
OL,13,Fthe toilets and bin stores.
OL,15,FThe water itself is crystal clear `
OL,16,Fnot drinkable but perfectly usable for
OL,17,Fwastewater like toilets.
